"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"People nowadays are crazy about the airdrops. It has become so easy to do scams.\\n\\n### \\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/aFbOAu6kq2Yj4m0LnbOy_.jpg?height=169&width=298)\\n\\nJust check out the public data , check what are people talking about on twitter, discord, reddit groups and make a rug project based on it.\\n\\nKeep 25% of the token supply for the so called core developers. And announce the project on twitter, pay some crypto influencers to talk about it. And wait until everybody on cryptotwitter goes crazy about it.\\n\\nEventually people will claim it and if you want people not to sell it straightaway then make some staking tool and show some roadmap of the \\\\*project\\\\*.\\n\\nGradually, the price of the token will rise. And when it has increased significantly, sell the tokens. Voila!\\n\\nWe should be careful about it and control our greed. The ruggers take benefits of our insecurities. We should condemn such activities and should totally ignore them ( as any publicity is good publicity )\\n\\n\\n---\\n\\nThank you for reading.\\n\\nPlease support me.\\n\\nFind me on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/alwaysbuzzboy) .\",\"timestamp\":1641884191,\"title\":\"Let's rug\\nHow easy it is to do scam\"},\"digest\":\"UajDd8qElqXtXH6UAQJf8oQutc7gaZwCGg7kUuIkTcI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xaef4842A2C6f44ed2D8C4BFf94451126D79A065E\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"7iCk2Qf_0NXU2ZM3KFUoeGBv5CL-CNgWnFvTu2WtppU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"0-WALfCP3BSw7PuJtgYkl80NnMpaA8WLmjaOPU0_kis\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"KGocwBztWe0JOCWs4zloNU6nVflreAtZpxnLmsObXpkKpgOCM-Fe5DHjVytTATc9GWfA9rJsYJC-rlnv4cliGA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xd68f95f7150f22cc4e62e2077f65c65a5e7cb4fbd48dbd62d0599be6696520c83081bdfccc7d98f8fe0ee7ce1af37c8b0d242fed051085485130d4b6359bd6761b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this d